      <title>部长称反对派推迟加拿大人工智能框架“令人尴尬”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-26/canada-s-lack-of-ai-framework-embarrassing-minister-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[加拿大工业部长表示，采用人工智能框架的持续挑战对该国来说并不乐观。如果总理贾斯汀·特鲁多的少数派政府比预期更早垮台，这项法律可能永远不会出台。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-26/canada-s-lack-of-ai-framework-embarrassing-minister-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 26 Sep 2024 15:41:23 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
